  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without a Dawn is a dark, psychological, and philosophical visual horror novel featuring hauntingly beautiful pseudo-ASCII art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She seeks refuge from her constant, restless thoughts in a remote cabin. There are no distractions in the profound silence and isolation, but the eerie sound of the cold wind weaving through the trees keeps her awake. In the dark stillness of the night, the silence has begun to take on physical form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without a Dawn masterfully immerses the player in introspection, intertwining psychological and philosophical elements to create a narrative that blurs the line between reality and fiction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/6ea39b5f9e48109ad5c8cefd6895e96b.gif?t=1767956222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/6ea39b5f9e48109ad5c8cefd6895e96b.poster.avif?t=1767956222\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The art style and audio are handcrafted and designed with extreme care and love.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Changeable color palettes, textures, and frames.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into a gripping narrative blurring the line between reality and fiction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a delicate philosophical and psychological introspection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handmade in Finland.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/7a40b53799d3006d54954db1a8bd5772.poster.avif?t=1767956222\" ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/7a40b53799d3006d54954db1a8bd5772.webm?t=1767956222\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >COMMUNITY FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without a Dawn can load and read fan localizations!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Create custom color palettes, frames, and textures!*</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without a Dawn can load and read external voice acting!*</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/a8adb2dc18d7b757b6c1b6c5a2edf712.gif?t=1767956222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/a8adb2dc18d7b757b6c1b6c5a2edf712.poster.avif?t=1767956222\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*Creating palettes, frames, and textures requires image editing software.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*External voice acting requires audio editing software.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>*See the game folder for documentation.</i></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/126b2f08be41dce2716830069dfc10ba.apng?t=1767956222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/126b2f08be41dce2716830069dfc10ba.poster.avif?t=1767956222\" class=\"bb_img\" width=512 height=64 /></picture></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Press kit for the press, content creators, and influencers can be located on the official homepage.</i></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without a Dawn is a dark, psychological, and philosophical visual horror novel featuring hauntingly beautiful pseudo-ASCII art.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She seeks refuge from her constant, restless thoughts in a remote cabin. There are no distractions in the profound silence and isolation, but the eerie sound of the cold wind weaving through the trees keeps her awake. In the dark stillness of the night, the silence has begun to take on physical form.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Without a Dawn masterfully immerses the player in introspection, intertwining psychological and philosophical elements to create a narrative that blurs the line between reality and fiction.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/6ea39b5f9e48109ad5c8cefd6895e96b.gif?t=1767956222\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3145620/extras/6ea39b5f9e48109ad5c8cefd6895e96b.poster.avif?t=1767956222\" class=\"bb_img\" /></picture></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The art style and audio are handcrafted and designed with extreme care and love.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Changeable color palettes, textures, and frames.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Delve into a gripping narrative blurring the line between reality and fiction.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Get ready for a delicate philosophical and psychological introspection.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Handmade in Finland.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https